<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2 class="heading-section">
      <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">/</span> About Me
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
          The Builder's Journey
        </h3>

        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I've been building things my whole life. The medium changes - the drive doesn't.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          At 21, I launched an energy shot company from scratch. I formulated the product, built the brand,
          sold thousands of bottles personally, and got on local television twice. I was in meetings with
          VitaminShoppe buyers when my supply chain collapsed overnight. That failure taught me more than
          any success could have.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          I pivoted to IT, taught myself everything, and earned my AWS Solutions Architect certification.
          No bootcamp. No CS degree. Just relentless learning and building.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          In August 2022 - three months before ChatGPT launched publicly - I was already building with the API.
          I've since worked with every major provider: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, DeepSeek, Kimi.
          I'm not just using AI tools; I'm building AI systems.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Today I'm a System Administrator by day and an AI platform builder by night. I'm looking for the
          right opportunity to bring everything together: the entrepreneurial grit, the technical depth,
          the customer-facing experience, and the genuine passion for building things that help people.
        </p>
      </div>

